John Winston (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Winston_(actor) 0 John Winston (born 24 October 1927 in Leeds, West Riding of Yorkshire) is an English actor known for his appearances as "Lieutenant Kyle", the Transporter Chief and occasional bridge officer in the original Star Trek series. Currently, he resides in North Hollywood, Los Angeles.
